The last three weeks have been the most agonizing for the family of security expert Mwenda Mbijiwe. The family has for the first time come out to speak about the disappearance of their kin who has been missing for three weeks now. According to Mbijjiwe's mother Jane Gatwiri, anonymous sources have confided in her that her son is alive and is now asking the government to expedite the process of searching for him.